# RQ-53-10-01-026: Temperature Probe Location

## Requirement Statement
The nose cone shall provide mounting for total air temperature (TAT) probes in appropriate locations.

## Acceptance Criteria
- 2 TAT probes (redundancy)
- Location in free stream airflow
- Minimal heating from structure
- Accuracy ±2°C

## Compliance Status
Design complete

## Traceability
Parent: ATA 34 (Air Data System)
